</p>

</div>
<div id="fn" class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#GEWN-03-01-02-0050-fn-0001-ptr" id="GEWN-03-01-02-0050-fn-0001">1</a>

   <p>GW reached Cambridge on 2 July. For an account of his journey from Philadelphia, see <a href="default.xqy?keys=GEWN-print-03-01-02-0048" class="document">GW to Hancock, 1011 July 1775</a>, <a href="default.xqy?keys=GEWN-print-03-01-02-0047-0003&amp;expandNote=GEWN-03-01-02-0047-0003-fn-0001#GEWN-03-01-02-0047-0003-fn-0001" class="document">Document II. Letter Sent, n.1</a>.</p>

</div>
<div class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#GEWN-03-01-02-0050-fn-0002-ptr" id="GEWN-03-01-02-0050-fn-0002">2</a>

   <p>For GWs attempts to obtain the returns wanted by Congress, see <a href="default.xqy?keys=GEWN-print-03-01-02-0041&amp;expandNote=GEWN-03-01-02-0041-fn-0003#GEWN-03-01-02-0041-fn-0003" class="document">General Orders, 8 July 1775, n.3</a>.</p>

</div>
<div class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#GEWN-03-01-02-0050-fn-0003-ptr" id="GEWN-03-01-02-0050-fn-0003">3</a>

   <p>See <a href="default.xqy?keys=GEWN-print-03-01-02-0045" class="document">Council of War, 9 July 1775</a>.</p>

</div>
<div class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#GEWN-03-01-02-0050-fn-0004-ptr" id="GEWN-03-01-02-0050-fn-0004">4</a>

   <p>For a discussion of the British reinforcements from Ireland, see ibid., n.3.</p>

